18#ifndef _LVM_CMDLINE_H
19#define _LVM_CMDLINE_H
20
21struct cmd_context;
22
23struct cmdline_context {
24 struct arg *the_args;
25 struct command *commands;
26 int num_commands;
27 int commands_size;
28 int interactive;
29};
30
31int lvm2_main(int argc, char **argv);
32
33void *cmdlib_lvm2_init(unsigned static_compile);
34void lvm_fin(struct cmd_context *cmd);
35
36struct cmd_context *init_lvm(void);
37void lvm_register_commands(void);
38int lvm_split(char *str, int *argc, char **argv, int max);
39int lvm_run_command(struct cmd_context *cmd, int argc, char **argv);
40int lvm_shell(struct cmd_context *cmd, struct cmdline_context *cmdline);
